        <p class="text-neutral-700">
          Spain wants to ensure non-lucrative visa holders won't become a burden on the public healthcare system. By requiring comprehensive, no-copay private insurance, they ensure you can access care without financial barriers and without relying on the Spanish public system. This protects both you and Spain's healthcare resources.
